WEBVTT

00:00:55.800 --> 00:01:00.936
so that we carry that suitcase
in our journey of life

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:04.296
and thus, be able to solve 
whatever problem we encounter.

00:01:04.319 --> 00:01:07.320
But this old model

00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:13.376
was changed by the internet.

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:16.936
Because now, our school,

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:21.460
our teachers, our books are in our pocket.

00:01:21.460 --> 00:01:23.080
(Laughter)

00:01:23.080 --> 00:01:29.200
Eighteen years ago,
I conducted a small experiment in Delhi.